# arvo-bits

Concrete trait impls for the bit-level contracts. Blanket impls of
`HasBitWidth`, `BitAccess`, `BitSequence`, `BitLogic`, `BitPrim`,
`UBitContainer`, `IBitContainer` (declared in `arvo-bits-contracts`)
on `Bits<N, S>` (from `arvo-storage`) and the bare primitive
containers (`u8`, `u16`, `u32`, `u64`, `i8`..`i64`). Hosts the
bit-storage aliases (`Bit`, `Nibble`, `Byte`, `Word`, `DWord`,
`QWord`) as typed `Bits<N, Hot>` newtypes for common widths.
`#![no_std]`, no alloc.
